Setup
-----

1. Insert passwords in ~/.mailpass-<account_name>.gpg
2. ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/mbsyncrc ~/.mbsyncrc && chmod 600 ~/.mbsyncrc
3. ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/notmuch-config ~/.notmuch-config && chmod 600 ~/.notmuch-config
4. ln -s ~/src/emacs.d/mail/notmuch-run ~/bin/notmuch-run && chmod 700 ~/bin/notmuch-run

Run
---

mbsync gmail && notmuch-run










mbsync + mu + mu4e + notmuch

